---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Polymarket — Prediction Market">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-24">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Prediction Market</span><span class="lang-zh">預測市場</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">Polymarket</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      <span class="lang-en">The dominant onchain prediction market — a hybrid-decentralized CLOB where every real-world event becomes a binary contract settled on Polygon. Not an AMM. A real order book with maker/taker dynamics, backed by UMA's optimistic oracle for resolution. ICE (NYSE's parent) has invested ~$2 billion. Price = market-implied probability, enforced by real money.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">最大嘅鏈上預測市場 — 一個hybrid-decentralized CLOB，每個真實世界事件都變成喺Polygon上結算嘅binary contract。唔係AMM，係真正嘅order book，有maker/taker dynamics，用UMA嘅optimistic oracle做resolution。ICE（NYSE母公司）已投資~$20億。價格 = market-implied probability，由真金白銀enforce。</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Stats grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-12">
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">$7B</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Monthly vol record (Feb 2026)</span><span class="lang-zh">月交易量紀錄（2026年2月）</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">$425M</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Single-day record</span><span class="lang-zh">單日最高</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">~$2B</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">ICE total investment</span><span class="lang-zh">ICE總投資</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">CLOB</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Not AMM — real order book</span><span class="lang-zh">唔係AMM — 真order book</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none text-zinc-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Unlike surveys or analyst opinions, prediction markets aggregate information through financial incentives. If you believe the market is mispricing an outcome, you have a direct way to profit from your conviction. Polymarket's 2024 US election pricing was closer to the final result than any major poll. Real money, skin in the game, proved more accurate than aggregated surveys and analyst consensus.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">唔同於survey或analyst opinion，預測市場通過經濟激勵嚟匯集信息。如果你認為市場對某個結果定價錯誤，你可以直接從你嘅判斷中獲利。Polymarket 2024年美國大選嘅定價比所有主流民調更接近最終結果。Real money，skin in the game，比匯總調查和分析師共識更準確。</span>
      </p>

      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <!-- How It Works -->
      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">How It Works — Binary Contracts</span><span class="lang-zh">點樣運作 — 二元合約</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Each market is a yes/no contract. Take "Fed will cut rates in June" — you buy YES at $0.65, meaning the market-implied probability is 65%. If the outcome is correct, the contract pays $1. If incorrect, it pays $0. Your maximum loss is the price you paid. No leverage, no liquidation, fully collateralized.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">每個market係一個yes/no contract。以「Fed will cut rates in June」為例 — 你以$0.65買YES，即market implied probability 65%。結果正確，合約付$1。錯誤，付$0。最大損失就係你付出嘅價格。冇槓桿，冇爆倉，全額抵押。</span>
      </p>

      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <!-- CTF Exchange -->
      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Architecture: The CTF Exchange (CLOB)</span><span class="lang-zh">架構：CTF Exchange（CLOB）</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Polymarket does <span class="text-white font-medium">not</span> use an AMM. It runs a <span class="text-white">Central Limit Order Book</span> (CLOB) called the CTF Exchange — a hybrid-decentralized system where order matching happens off-chain for speed, but settlement is executed non-custodially on Polygon via EIP-712 signed messages.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Polymarket<span class="text-white font-medium">唔係</span>用AMM。佢跑一個叫CTF Exchange嘅<span class="text-white">Central Limit Order Book</span>（CLOB）— 一個hybrid-decentralized系統，order matching喺off-chain進行以確保速度，但settlement通過EIP-712 signed messages喺Polygon上non-custodially執行。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The operator validates signatures, checks balances, verifies tick size compliance, matches marketable orders immediately, and submits matched trades on-chain for atomic settlement. Non-marketable orders rest on the book until filled or cancelled. <span class="text-white">You never give up custody of your funds</span> — the Exchange contract transfers tokens directly between wallets.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Operator驗證簽名、檢查餘額、驗證tick size合規性、即時matching可成交orders，然後將matched trades提交到鏈上做atomic settlement。未成交orders留喺book上面直到fill或取消。<span class="text-white">你永遠唔使放棄資金控制權</span> — Exchange contract直接喺錢包之間轉移tokens。</span>
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Order Types</span><span class="lang-zh">訂單類型</span>
      </h3>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto -mx-2">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800">
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Type</span><span class="lang-zh">類型</span></th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Behavior</span><span class="lang-zh">行為</span></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-zinc-400">
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white">GTC</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Good-Til-Cancelled — rests on book until filled or cancelled</span><span class="lang-zh">Good-Til-Cancelled — 留喺book直到fill或取消</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white">GTD</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Good-Til-Date — auto-expires at specified timestamp</span><span class="lang-zh">Good-Til-Date — 喺指定時間戳自動到期</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white">FOK</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Fill-Or-Kill — fill entirely and immediately, or cancel</span><span class="lang-zh">Fill-Or-Kill — 即時全部fill，否則取消</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white">FAK</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Fill-And-Kill — fill what's available now, cancel the rest</span><span class="lang-zh">Fill-And-Kill — 即時fill可用部分，取消剩餘</span></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Tick sizes: <code>0.1</code>, <code>0.01</code>, <code>0.001</code>, or <code>0.0001</code> — each market has a specific tick size. Orders that don't conform are rejected. Tick size can change dynamically when price moves above 0.96 or below 0.04.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Tick sizes：<code>0.1</code>、<code>0.01</code>、<code>0.001</code>或<code>0.0001</code> — 每個market有特定嘅tick size。唔符合嘅orders會被reject。價格去到0.96以上或0.04以下時tick size可以動態改變。</span>
      </p>

      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <!-- Conditional Token Framework -->
      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Conditional Token Framework — How Tokens Are Created</span><span class="lang-zh">Conditional Token Framework — Token點樣創建</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Built on the <span class="text-white">Gnosis Conditional Token Framework</span> — an open standard that tokenizes outcomes as ERC-1155 tokens on Polygon. Every YES/NO pair is backed by exactly <span class="text-white">$1.00 USDC.e</span> locked in the CTF contract. Full collateralization, always.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">建基於<span class="text-white">Gnosis Conditional Token Framework</span> — 一個開放標準，將結果代幣化為Polygon上嘅ERC-1155 tokens。每對YES/NO都由精確嘅<span class="text-white">$1.00 USDC.e</span>鎖定喺CTF contract入面支撐。永遠全額抵押。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Three core operations:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">三個核心操作：</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Split</span> — deposit $1 USDC.e → receive 1 YES + 1 NO token</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">Split</span> — 存入$1 USDC.e → 收到1個YES + 1個NO token</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Merge</span> — return 1 YES + 1 NO → receive $1 USDC.e back</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">Merge</span> — 交還1個YES + 1個NO → 取回$1 USDC.e</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Redeem</span> — after resolution, winning tokens redeem for $1 each (losing tokens = worthless)</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">Redeem</span> — resolution之後，贏嘅tokens兌換$1（輸嘅tokens = 冇價值）</span></li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">How minting works in practice:</span> Bettor X wants YES at $0.60, Bettor Y wants NO at $0.40. Combined = $1.00 locked as collateral. 1 YES token minted to X, 1 NO token minted to Y. The CLOB handles this matching automatically.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">實際minting運作：</span>Bettor X想以$0.60買YES，Bettor Y想以$0.40買NO。合計 = $1.00鎖定做collateral。1個YES token mint畀X，1個NO token mint畀Y。CLOB自動處理matching。</span>
      </p>

      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <!-- UMA Oracle -->
      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Resolution: UMA Optimistic Oracle</span><span class="lang-zh">結算：UMA Optimistic Oracle</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">When a market's event concludes, resolution happens through UMA's <span class="text-white">three-layer optimistic oracle</span>:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">當market嘅事件結束時，resolution通過UMA嘅<span class="text-white">三層optimistic oracle</span>進行：</span>
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-6 mt-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-cyan-950 border border-cyan-800 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0">1</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-1"><span class="lang-en">Proposal</span><span class="lang-zh">提案</span></p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm"><span class="lang-en">Anyone posts an outcome + <span class="text-white">$750 USDC.e bond</span>. This starts the clock.</span><span class="lang-zh">任何人提交結果 + <span class="text-white">$750 USDC.e���證金</span>。時鐘開始計時。</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-cyan-950 border border-cyan-800 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0">2</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-1"><span class="lang-en">Challenge Period (2 hours)</span><span class="lang-zh">挑戰期（2小時）</span></p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm"><span class="lang-en">Anyone can dispute by posting a counter-bond of $750. If no dispute, the proposal auto-accepts. ~98.5% of markets resolve here without escalation.</span><span class="lang-zh">任何人可以提交$750反保證金嚟dispute。如果冇dispute，proposal自動接受。~98.5%嘅markets喺呢度resolve，唔使升級。</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-cyan-950 border border-cyan-800 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0">3</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-1"><span class="lang-en">DVM Vote (if disputed)</span><span class="lang-zh">DVM投票（如有爭議）</span></p>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm"><span class="lang-en">First dispute: market resets, new request issued. Second dispute: escalates to UMA <span class="text-white">Data Verification Mechanism</span> — token holders vote over ~48 hours. Winner gets their bond back + half the loser's bond.</span><span class="lang-zh">第一次dispute：market重置，發出新request。第二次dispute：升級到UMA <span class="text-white">Data Verification Mechanism</span> — token holders投票，約48小時。贏家攞返保證金 + 輸家保證金嘅一半。</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4">
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Edge cases:</span> If neither YES nor NO is appropriate, a <span class="text-white">50/50 resolution</span> makes each token redeem for $0.50. "Too Early" proposals (before event concludes) automatically lose their bond. Polymarket is non-custodial and <span class="text-white">cannot alter or reverse</span> resolutions once finalized by UMA.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">邊緣情況：</span>如果YES同NO都唔啱，<span class="text-white">50/50 resolution</span>令每個token兌換$0.50。「Too Early」嘅提案（事件未結束前提交）自動輸保證金。Polymarket係non-custodial，UMA finalize之後<span class="text-white">唔能更改或逆轉</span>resolution。</span>
      </p>

      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <!-- Multi-Outcome Markets -->
      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Multi-Outcome (Negative Risk) Markets</span><span class="lang-zh">多結果（Negative Risk）市場</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Not all markets are binary. <span class="text-white">Negative risk markets</span> are mutually exclusive multi-outcome events — e.g., "Who wins the election?" with 5 candidates. Each outcome has its own binary market, but <span class="text-white">only one can resolve YES</span>; all others resolve NO. YES prices across all outcomes should approximately sum to $1.00.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">唔係所有market都係binary。<span class="text-white">Negative risk markets</span>係互斥嘅多結果事件 — 例如「邊個贏選舉？」有5個候選人。每個結果有自己嘅binary market，但<span class="text-white">只有一個會resolve YES</span>；其他全部resolve NO。所有結果嘅YES價格加埋應該約等於$1.00。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Key mechanic:</span> A NO share in any market can be <span class="text-white">atomically converted</span> into 1 YES share in every other market via the Neg Risk Adapter contract. Example: holding 1 NO on "0 rate cuts" = holding 1 YES on each of {1, 2, 3, ..., 8+} rate cuts. This creates arbitrage-free pricing across all outcomes.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">關鍵機制：</span>任何market嘅NO share可以通過Neg Risk Adapter contract<span class="text-white">原子轉換</span>為其他所有market嘅1個YES share。例子：持有1個「0次減息」NO = 持有{1、2、3、...、8+}次減息嘅各1個YES。呢個創建咗跨所有結果嘅無套利定價。</span>
      </p>

      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <!-- Fee Structure -->
      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Fee Structure</span><span class="lang-zh">費用結構</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Makers pay zero fees.</span> Only takers pay. Fee formula: <code>fee = shares × feeRate × p × (1-p)</code> — fees peak at 50% probability and decrease toward both extremes. A trade at $0.30 costs the same fee as one at $0.70.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">Maker零手續費。</span>只有taker付費。費用公式：<code>fee = shares × feeRate × p × (1-p)</code> — 費用喺50%概率時最高，向兩個極端遞減。以$0.30交易嘅費用同以$0.70交易嘅一樣。</span>
      </p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto -mx-2 mt-4">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800">
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Category</span><span class="lang-zh">類別</span></th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Taker Fee Rate</span><span class="lang-zh">Taker費率</span></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-zinc-400">
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white">Crypto</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2">7.2%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white"><span class="lang-en">Finance / Politics / Tech</span><span class="lang-zh">金融 / 政治 / 科技</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2">4%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white"><span class="lang-en">Economics / Culture</span><span class="lang-zh">經濟 / 文化</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2">5%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white">Sports</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2">3%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white"><span class="lang-en">Geopolitics</span><span class="lang-zh">地緣政治</span></td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-green-400"><span class="lang-en">Free (0%)</span><span class="lang-zh">免費（0%）</span></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4">
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Maker rebates:</span> 100% of collected taker fees are redistributed daily to market makers, proportional to their share of executed maker liquidity in each market. Separate <span class="text-white">liquidity rewards program</span> pays additional USDC to resting limit orders using quadratic scoring — orders closer to the midpoint earn more.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">Maker返利：</span>100%收取到嘅taker費用每日按比例分配畀market makers。另外嘅<span class="text-white">流動性獎勵計劃</span>用quadratic scoring向resting limit orders額外派USDC — 越接近midpoint嘅orders賺越多。</span>
      </p>

      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <!-- Available Markets -->
      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Available Markets</span><span class="lang-zh">可交易市場</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Market coverage is broad and growing. Macro markets track Fed rate decisions (updating faster than CME FedWatch), Trump executive orders, and geopolitical outcomes. Sports generates ~$120M daily across NBA, NFL, soccer. The fastest-growing category is AI with 535+ active markets. Culture covers Oscars, Grammys, celebrity events.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">市場覆蓋範圍廣泛且持續增長。宏觀市場追蹤Fed利率決定（更新速度比CME FedWatch更快）、Trump行政命令同地緣政治結果。體育每日~$1.2億交易量，覆蓋NBA、NFL、足球。增長最快嘅類別係AI，有535+活躍市場。文化覆蓋奧斯卡、Grammy、名人事件。</span>
      </p>

      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <!-- API & Programmatic Trading -->
      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">API & Programmatic Trading</span><span class="lang-zh">API同程序化交易</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">A significant share of Polymarket volume comes from algorithmic traders. The platform provides three APIs:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Polymarket嘅交易量有相當部分嚟自algo traders。平台提供三個API：</span>
      </p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto -mx-2">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800">
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium">API</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Purpose</span><span class="lang-zh">用途</span></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-zinc-400">
            <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
              <td class="py-3 px-2 text-white">CLOB API</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-2"><span class="lang-en">Trading, orders, order book depth</span><span class="lang-zh">交易、訂單、order book深度</span></td>
            </tr>
